OL,6,FVideo report about the SAS by ITN
OL,7,Fcorrespondent Paul Davies.
OL,9,FA Liverpool-born SAS man involved in
OL,10,Fthe daring attack to free hostages
OL,11,Ffrom the Iranian Embassy in 1980 has
OL,12,Fdied at the age of 82.
