OL,6,FThe death of John Thompson was
OL,7,Fannounced on the Facebook page of the
OL,8,FParachute Regiment and Airborne Forces
OL,9,FMemorial Group, which said: "It is
OL,10,Fwith great sadness that I share the
OL,11,Fnews of the passing of John Thompson
OL,12,Flast night. John was an extraordinary
OL,13,Findividual whose impact on those
OL,14,Faround him will not be forgotten...
