OL,6,F"...John served with honor in the 16
OL,7,FParachute Brigade and the renowned 22
OL,8,FSAS Regiment. He was a proud
OL,9,Fparticipant in Operation Nimrod during
OL,10,Fthe Iranian Embassy siege, showcasing
OL,11,Fhis bravery and commitment to his
OL,12,Fcountry."
OL,14,FThe Iranian Embassy siege took place
OL,15,Ffrom 30 April to 5 May 1980, and was
OL,16,Ftelevised live on domestic television.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
