OL,3,CSAS man who helped free Iranian
OL,4,CEmbassy hostages dies aged 82
OL,6,FIt saw six armed SAS men, dressed in
OL,7,Fblack, storm the Embassy in South
OL,8,FKensington in London after
OL,9,Fnegotiations with the hostage takers
OL,10,Fhad reached stalemate.
OL,12,FThe gunmen inside were Iranian Arabs
OL,13,Fcampaigning for sovereignty of a
OL,14,Fprovince of Iran called Khuzestan.
OL,15,FThey had taken 26 people hostage and
OL,16,Fwere demanding prisoner releases and
OL,17,Ftheir own safe passage from the UK.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
