OL,3,CSAS man who helped free Iranian
OL,4,CEmbassy hostages dies aged 82
OL,6,FAs the siege developed into its sixth
OL,7,Fday, five hostages were released but
OL,8,Fas tension grew, one hostage was
OL,9,Fkilled and his body thrown out of the
OL,10,Fbuilding.
OL,12,FIn a raid known as Operation Nimrod,
OL,13,Fthe SAS(Special Air Service) attacked
OL,14,Fthe Embassy to rescue the remaining
OL,15,Fhostages by abseiling from the roof
OL,16,Fand forcing entry through the windows.
OL,18,FIn total, the attack lasted just 17
OL,19,Fminutes and saw all but one of the
OL,20,Fremaining hostages freed and five of
OL,21,Fthe six hostage-takers killed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
