OL,6,FJohn Thompson enlisted in the REME
OL,7,F(Royal Electrical Mechanical
OL,8,FEngineers) of the Parachute Brigade
OL,9,Fand later the SAS. He also served in
OL,10,Fthe Falklands War and reached the rank
OL,11,Fof Warrant Officer. He later went on
OL,12,Fto serve in the Omani Army.
OL,14,FAfter retiring from the forces, John
OL,15,Ftrekked to the Mount Everest Base
OL,16,FCamp, completed numerous marathons and
OL,17,Fultra marathons, and achieved a Black
OL,18,FBelt in martial arts. He spent his
OL,19,Flater years in Anglesey, North Wales.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
