OL,6,FHe visited Stockport to officially
OL,7,Fopen the HQ of RECCE HQ - a charity to
OL,8,Fsupport military veterans.
OL,10,FThe tribute on the memorial page went
OL,11,Fon: "One of the proudest moments for
OL,12,FJohn was receiving the veterans'
OL,13,FLifetime Achievement Award, a
OL,14,Frecognition that his daughter
OL,15,Fdescribed as one of the proudest days
OL,16,Fof her life.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
