OL,6,F"John's adventurous spirit, dedication
OL,7,Fto his family, and commitment to
OL,8,Fservice will continue to inspire us
OL,9,Fall. Though he may no longer be with
OL,10,Fus, his legacy will live on in the
OL,11,Fhearts and minds of everyone he
OL,12,Ftouched.
OL,14,F"Rest in peace, John Thompson. Your
OL,15,Fbravery and spirit will never be
OL,16,Fforgotten."
